 <li>(for final selection), University Advancement (once selected by President)&nbsp;</li> 
 <li><strong>Individuals in Bank</strong>: candidates and selected recipients of honourary degrees&nbsp;</li> 
 <li><strong>Retention and Disposal</strong>:&nbsp;<strong>Indefinitely</strong></li> 
